shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras/puzzles2.gif?t=1739554643\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The monster, which can be controlled by a player, or AI, needs to use its abilities to hunt down survivors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Monsters' skills can be used to gain energy, locate survivors, facilitate the hunt, or delay survivors' advance while scaring them simultaneously.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When a monster is full of energy, it can transform into its physical form to kill the survivors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras/multiplayers.gif?t=1739554643\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Immersive Audio Visual experience:</strong>  Damned 2 uses Unreal Engine 5 to bring graphics and audio immersion to a new level of horror.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Immersive VOIP:</strong> Our built in VOIP system simulates echos, reverberation and the environment around you. But be aware, monsters can hear you when they are hunting!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Be the Monster!:</strong> Choose from a variety of different monsters to play and scare your friends, each monster has a set of abilities for you to hunt and eliminate the trespassers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Co-operate:</strong> Play together with your friends with up to 5 players where teamwork is key for fast puzzle solving and exploration.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Randomized Environments &amp; Puzzles:</strong> Each play through is never the same. Keys, items and puzzles are placed in different locations whenever you start a new match.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Custom Difficulty:</strong> Choose your game settings before starting a new match, customize the way you want to play.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_p